# STARKLINGS

### The aim of this tutorial is to explore the Cairo language and Starknet.

This repository already includes the solutions to the exercises, but you can find the original repository to practise via <a href="https://github.com/shramee/starklings-cairo1">this link</a> if you are working with a shell or Visual Studio Code, or via <a href="https://starklings.app/">this link</a> if you prefer to practise via the web-based tutorial.
